OL,3,CRNLI warning over rip currents after
OL,4,Cfour swimmers rescued in Cornwall
OL,6,FRNLI lifeguards in Cornwall are
OL,7,Fwarning over rip current dangers after
OL,8,Fa rescue at Tregantle.
OL,10,FOn Wednesday 8 April, RNLI lifeguards
OL,11,Fand Looe RNLI volunteer lifeboats were
OL,12,Fcalled after four swimmers were
OL,13,Fspotted in difficulty near Longsands.
OL,15,FThe incident was described as 'severe'
OL,16,Fwith RNLI lifeguards requesting
OL,17,Fadditional support via Falmouth
OL,18,FCoastguard Maritime Rescue
OL,19,FCoordination Centre.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
