CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1775909467
OL,3,CRNLI warning over rip currents after
OL,4,Cfour swimmers rescued in Cornwall
OL,6,FAll swimmers were safely returned to
OL,7,Fshore.
OL,9,FVolunteer Lifeboat Operations Manager
OL,10,FClive Palfrey commended the teamwork
OL,11,Fbetween services.
OL,13,F"The lifeguards made exactly the right
OL,14,Fcall by requesting support from Looe
OL,15,FRNLI D class lifeboat, the most
OL,16,Fsuitable asset for surf zone rescues.
OL,18,F"In fastmoving situations like this,
OL,19,Fknowing a lifeboat is on the way
OL,20,Fallows lifeguards to focus entirely on
OL,21,Fthe rescue in front of them."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
