OL,3,CRNLI warning over rip currents after
OL,4,Cfour swimmers rescued in Cornwall
OL,6,F"Even the most experienced beachgoers
OL,7,Fcan be caught out by rips, so don't be
OL,8,Fafraid to ask lifeguards for advice."
OL,10,FThe RNLI advice for those who get
OL,11,Fcaught in a rip is:
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
